 cr\u00e9ativit\u00e9: De l\u2019analyse des facteurs cognitifs \u00e0 l\u2019assistance aux activit\u00e9s de conception cr\u00e9atives. Le travail humain <strong class=\"EmphasisTypeBold \">72</strong>(1), 5 (2009). <span class=\"ExternalRef\">\u00a0<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.3917/th.721.0005\"><span class=\"RefSource\">https://doi.org/10.3917/th.721.0005</span></a></span><span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceDOI\"><a class=\"gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"CrossRef\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.3917/th.721.0005\"><span><span>CrossRef</span></span></a></span><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Activit%C3%A9s%20de%20conception%20et%20cr%C3%A9ativit%C3%A9%3A%20De%20l%E2%80%99analyse%20des%20facteurs%20cognitifs%20%C3%A0%20l%E2%80%99assistance%20aux%20activit%C3%A9s%20de%20conception%20cr%C3%A9atives&amp;author=N.%20Bonnardel&amp;journal=Le%20travail%20humain&amp;volume=72&amp;issue=1&amp;pages=5&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;doi=10.3917%2Fth.721.0005\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR40\">Bornet, C.: Evaluation de la m\u00e9thode des personas en intervention corrective, pr\u00e9ventive et prospective. Universit\u00e9 de Lorraine (2014)<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Bornet%2C%20C.%3A%20Evaluation%20de%20la%20m%C3%A9thode%20des%20personas%20en%20intervention%20corrective%2C%20pr%C3%A9ventive%20et%20prospective.%20Universit%C3%A9%20de%20Lorraine%20%282014%29\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span>